  "keyFeatures": [
    "Present any SwiftUI view as a popover with a single modifier",
    "Supports both SwiftUI (.popover modifier) and UIKit (Popover instance)",
    "Absolute positioning (attached to source view) and relative/picture-in-picture positioning",
    "Smooth animated transitions between multiple popovers",
    "Highly customizable Attributes struct (position, animation, dismissal, accessibility)",
    "Drop-in system Menu replacement that works on iOS 13+",
    "Frame tagging system for referencing view frames across the hierarchy",
    "Full VoiceOver accessibility support",
    "Multiple screen and multitasking window support on iPadOS",
    "Zero external dependencies"
  ],
